parameters.description: Log of COTS population growth rate (year⁻¹). Corresponds to r_cots ≈ 2.0, representing potential for rapid population growth during outbreaks.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Crown of Thorns starfish population exponential growth potential

parameters.description: Log of COTS carrying capacity (individuals/m²). Corresponds to K_cots ≈ 2.0, representing maximum sustainable density.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Maximum sustainable Crown of Thorns starfish population density

parameters.description: Log of temperature effect on COTS reproduction (dimensionless). Controls steepness of temperature response curve.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Sea temperature's nonlinear impact on starfish reproductive success

parameters.description: Log of temperature threshold for COTS reproduction (°C). Corresponds to ~28°C, above which COTS reproduction increases.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Critical sea temperature triggering Crown of Thorns reproduction

parameters.description: Log of effect of larval immigration on COTS recruitment (dimensionless). Scales the impact of external larval supply.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: External larval immigration influence on starfish population recruitment

parameters.description: Log of intrinsic growth rate of fast-growing coral (year⁻¹). Corresponds to r_fast ≈ 0.5, representing annual growth rate of Acropora spp.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Fast-growing Acropora coral annual regeneration and recovery rate

parameters.description: Log of intrinsic growth rate of slow-growing coral (year⁻¹). Corresponds to r_slow ≈ 0.2, representing annual growth rate of Faviidae and Porites spp.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Slow-growing massive coral species annual regeneration potential

parameters.description: Log of carrying capacity of fast-growing coral (%). Corresponds to K_fast ≈ 50%, maximum potential cover for Acropora spp.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Maximum potential cover for branching Acropora coral species

parameters.description: Log of carrying capacity of slow-growing coral (%). Corresponds to K_slow ≈ 40%, maximum potential cover for slow-growing species.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Maximum potential cover for slow-growing massive coral species

parameters.description: Log of attack rate on fast-growing coral (m²/individual/year). Corresponds to a_fast ≈ 0.1, representing COTS preference for Acropora spp.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Crown of Thorns predation rate on fast-growing branching corals

parameters.description: Log of attack rate on slow-growing coral (m²/individual/year). Corresponds to a_slow ≈ 0.05, representing lower COTS preference for slow-growing species.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Crown of Thorns predation rate on slow-growing massive corals

parameters.description: Log of handling time for fast-growing coral (year/%). Corresponds to h_fast ≈ 0.01, time spent consuming Acropora spp.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Handling time for consuming fast-growing branching coral species

parameters.description: Log of handling time for slow-growing coral (year/%). Corresponds to h_slow ≈ 0.02, longer time spent consuming tougher slow-growing species.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Handling time for consuming slow-growing massive coral species

parameters.description: Log of coral cover effect on COTS survival (dimensionless). Corresponds to coral_effect ≈ 10, half-saturation constant for coral-dependent survival.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Coral cover's impact on Crown of Thorns starfish population survival

parameters.description: Log of observation error SD for COTS. Corresponds to sigma_cots ≈ 0.2, representing measurement error in COTS surveys.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Measurement uncertainty in Crown of Thorns starfish population surveys

parameters.description: Log of observation error SD for fast-growing coral. Corresponds to sigma_fast ≈ 0.5, representing measurement error in coral cover surveys.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Measurement uncertainty in fast-growing coral cover assessments

parameters.description: Log of observation error SD for slow-growing coral. Corresponds to sigma_slow ≈ 0.5, representing measurement error in coral cover surveys.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Measurement uncertainty in slow-growing coral cover assessments

parameters.description: Log of predation rate on COTS (year⁻¹). Corresponds to pred_rate ≈ 0.1, representing the baseline mortality rate due to natural predators.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Natural predation pressure on Crown of Thorns starfish populations
